en-US.title: KC CARE Health Center
en-US.description: KC CARE Health Center provides whole-person care, including medical services, behavioural health, and testing services. They are particularly catered to serving the transgender community with specific services like transgender health and sexual health. KC CARE promotes health equality and believes in healthcare as a right for everyone.

address: 3515 Broadway Blvd, Kansas City, MO 64111, USA
